<title>Codex Scrolls Index</title>
<style>
body { font-family: system-ui; padding: 24px; max-width: 900px; margin: auto }
code { background: #111; color: #c8ffc8; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 6px }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Codex Scrolls Index ‚Äî v241.x</h1>
<ul>
<li>sotolios_yhwh_apollonius.md ‚Äî <code>d4b9c7e25e3a‚Ä¶</code></li>
<li>lineage_codex.json ‚Äî <code>3c2a64be7421‚Ä¶</code></li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>


