‚úÖ Deploy Steps

1. Copy this structure into your GitHub repo root.


2. Commit everything:

git add .
git commit -m "v241.x Living Scrolls"
git push


3. Run:

python scrolls/build_scrolls.py

to regenerate hashes and HTML whenever scrolls are updated.




